::KitKat::

She walked to the lab and found some bandages.  She walked over to 
Land Mine. She put the bandages on Land Mine."There now.  Now no more 
cutting on yourself and I'll give you the blade back."
She took out hte knife and handed it to Land Mine.
"NOw, plese tell me why you were cutting on yourself? I know things 
aren't so good now and it can get to you.  But understand that 
someday, things will be different.  I'm not sure how or when.  But it 
will.  You just worry about staying alive and unharmed.  I'l look out 
for the rest." She smiled at Land Mine. "OK?"
